{"tid":761162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"4萬人湧「天空之鏡」 茶卡鹽湖變垃圾場","createTime":"2018-07-30T07:07:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T12:11:41.000Z","uid":75969,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c3250f6125b1d18e9823c720bff7f9c28c495eb5","tid":761162,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:07:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180729/large/1532873190_9561.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180729%2Flarge%2F1532873190_9561.jpg&h=35117e68&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">每日有4萬人湧到茶卡鹽湖，遊客亂扔用過的鞋套，令景區垃圾成災。</span><br />\n<br />\n被稱為「中國天空之鏡」、位於青海烏蘭縣的茶卡鹽湖，暑假期間每日約有4萬遊客湧至。遊客人多，垃圾自然多，當地遊客完全無視垃圾桶，將用過的鞋套隨地亂扔，工作人員每日工作13小時，都無法清理這些垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n這個面積105平方公里的鹽湖，除了被稱為「中國天空之鏡」，更被國家旅遊地理雜誌評為「人一生必去的55個地方」之一，每年都吸引大量遊客。原來景區人員不准遊客踏足鹽湖的，不過今年推出新規定，遊客只要在景區購買鞋套或者雨靴，便可以踏入鹽湖裏。<br />\n<br />\n可是，遊覽過後遊客都將脫下來的鞋套隨手亂扔，即使景區設置大量垃圾桶、工作人員不斷廣播，遊客仍然無視廣播。有工作人員甚至要將部份範圍封閉，以便他們收集堆積如山的鞋套。<br />\n「我是真看不過這種隨手拋垃圾的人！」不少曾經去過的網民，均大罵這些遊客實在沒有公德心，「是不是要給這種人手上綁個垃圾桶才好？」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180729/large/1532873355_4e54.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180729%2Flarge%2F1532873355_4e54.jpg&h=a9a01429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">遊客落水後，鞋套扔在地上。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180729/large/1532873356_de43.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180729%2Flarge%2F1532873356_de43.jpg&h=716ab899&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">鞋套被扔在湖邊。<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180730/58501080\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180730%2F58501080&d=utShODpQ9FEitk4nhvuj3TA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=72aae479\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180730%2F58501080&h=72f17153\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180730/58501080</a>"},{"pid":"3c080416c24c024e584ad5421bb0586b1016a731","tid":761162,"uid":1713,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:09:36.000Z","msg":"富有中國特色的天空之鏡"},{"pid":"6b78b069651ade8a7cb784687639507f84be8ad0","tid":761162,"uid":156363,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:11:59.000Z","msg":"好彩唔係玻利維亞果個"},{"pid":"b124d2d5492ecd1098cc6683414c063c4c8b1cb6","tid":761162,"uid":62532,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"6b78b069651ade8a7cb784687639507f84be8ad0","tid":761162,"uid":156363,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:11:59.000Z","msg":"好彩唔係玻利維亞果個"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:14:07.000Z","msg":"咪係 嚇死我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e4e34b9fd36d1e4e0a6063dc7f85ff9ea94ca07","tid":761162,"uid":20602,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:14:22.000Z","msg":"你又要賺啲鞋套錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d46f19aae39e41ee95f3188f14d454d6fe89bd1","tid":761162,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T07:14:53.000Z","msg":"支那豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"